title: Pacific Horizons (PAL) .iso
description:
PACIFIC HORIZONS - exploring the northwest coast by kayak
==========================================================

Showcasing some of the world's sought after sea kayaking destinations, Pacific Horizons captures the essence of the Ocean and inspires everyone to get out and
go kayaking! Blending wildlife, people, places and actionpacked kayaking, Bryan Smith takes us on an unforgettable journey documenting impressive tidal race surfing, the Orca whales of the San Juan Islands, the Bunsby Islands off Vancouver Island's remote and wild west coast, "commando kayaking" with Greenland rolling and ropes gymnastics champion Dubside, the wind and waves of Oregon's coast and Columbia River Gorge, a record setting circumnavigation of Vancouver Island, and to top it all off, a teaser of Justine Curgenven's film work depicting her journey around the Queen Charlotte Islands with Shawna Franklin and Leon Somme. Pacific Horizons is an entertaining, breath-taking, and inspirational adventure film.

Bonus material includes a full director's cut with details from behind the scenes!
